<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">מלחמה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
מלחמה / milchâmâh / mil-khaw-maw'

===Etymology===
From [[לחם]] {{HH|3898}} (in the sense of fighting); 

===Noun===
'''מלחמה'''

# a [[battle]] (that is, the engagement); generally war (that is, warfare): - battle, fight, (-ing), war ([-rior]).

